title: BullFrog Kench
body:
http://i1219.photobucket.com/albums/dd423/axe11154/Bull%20Frog%20Kench_zps59gqxxd4.jpg


I know the picture isnt the best lol but I had a idea and had to make it. BullFrog kench would be the first kench with out his whiskers. Basically the thought for him came in when I was thinking about cannibalistic bull frogs and how they will eat literally anything.... I had one for a pet once and his bite hurt. These guys don't have teeth, just snappy gums and a sticky tongue. They are literally the real work tahm kench in small green form. So while the drawing may not be the greatest, maybe you can agree, the idea is perfect for a skin for him.
